description: Unexploded bombs and other ordinance are hidden throughout Gaza posing a threat to civilians now and they will continue to potentially kill long after the war is over. We hear about a victim of one of these munitions and of the challenges of removing such threats as civilians are fleeing fighting.
title: The Deadly, Hidden Threat to Gaza's Civilians

description: The border collie-papillon mix got a round of "app-paws" for her surprise win after finishing the race in under 30 seconds. She is the first mixed-breed and first 12-inch dog to win the competition.
title: Small but mighty Nimble becomes first mixed-breed dog to win Westminster agility title

description: The huge container ship that struck the Key Bridge had electrical problems the day before it left the Port of Baltimore, according to a preliminary report released Tuesday by federal investigators.
title: The ship that struck the Key Bridge had electrical problems in port, the NTSB says

description: Caitlin Clark has sold out arenas nationwide. But can she, alongside 2023's Rookie of the Year Aliyah Boston, turn around the league's worst team? Or will the Las Vegas Aces pull off a three-peat?
title: What to watch for as the WNBA season opens and interest spikes in women's basketball

description: The bus was transporting 53 farmworkers at about 6:40 a.m. when it collided with a truck in Marion County, about 80 miles north of Orlando, the Florida Highway Patrol said.
title: 8 are dead and dozens injured as a bus carrying farmworkers overturns in Florida

description: The courtroom has continued to be one of the main arenas for Trump's 2024 campaign, welcoming his allies from across the country in for a day of testimony.
title: Trump gets by with a little help from his friends during New York hush money trial

description: It's rare for Israelis and Palestinians to join together for any reason during these days of war. But some did so this week for a ceremony honoring victims from all sides of the Israel-Hamas conflict.
title: Israelis and Palestinians held a joint memorial for all victims of the ongoing war

description: The Justice Department is expected to argue that its clamp down on TikTok is about national security, but Constitutional lawyers say there is no way around grappling with the free speech implications.
title: Legal experts say a TikTok ban without specific evidence violates the First Amendment

description: The United Nations said that one of its aid workers was killed and another injured when their vehicle was struck on Monday in Rafah in southern Gaza.
title: Strike kills U.N. aid worker, injures another in southern Gaza

description: He once boasted of being Donald Trump's "protector" but now he is testifying to lying for Trump's benefit, including about payments made to an adult film star ahead of the 2016 election.
title: Michael Cohen, a key witness in the Trump hush money trial, returns to the stand

description: After a pair of resignations rocked the pageant world, organizers have found a replacement for Miss USA but not Miss Teen USA. Last year's runner-up said this week that she turned down the crown.
title: Fallout continues from the Miss USA resignations as a runner-up declines the crown

description: New Yorkers and tourists alike stand in line outside the Manhattan criminal court with hopes of securing a spot in one of the rooms where the trial against former President Donald Trump can be viewed.
title: These people waited hours to see the Trump hush-money trial up close. Here's why

description: The state covers basic services for vulnerable residents, including things like air purifiers for kids with asthma. But nonprofits offering the services struggle to work within the health care system.
title: California's $12 billion Medicaid experiment stretches the definition of health care

description: President Biden will announce tariffs on $18 million of Chinese imports. Trump's lawyers will cross-examine Michael Cohen today in the former president's hush money trial.
title: Biden to announce new Chinese tariffs; Michael Cohen returns to the stand

description: AI can conjure the voice or likeness of a dead celebrity with just a few clicks. This opens a host of legal questions about the rights of the deceased and their heirs to control their digital replicas
title: It was a classic rap beef. Then Drake revived Tupac with AI and Congress got involved

description: Social media discourse and the inevitable backlash aside, the 26-year-old writer's first book is an amusing, if uneven, take on growing up white, privileged, and Gen Z.
title: What are 'the kids' thinking these days? Honor Levy aims to tell in 'My First Book'

description: There are clear similarities between 1968 and 2024, from presidential elections and anti-war protests to new Planet of the Apes movies. But historians tell NPR there are some key differences too.
title: Anti-war protests, a Chicago DNC: Is it 1968 all over again? Some historians say no

description: President Biden is keeping the tariffs on Chinese imports put in place by his predecessor and 2024 opponent, former President Donald Trump. And he's adding new ones for things like electric vehicles.
title: Biden announces new tariffs on imports of Chinese goods, including electric vehicles

description: A Jesus made of vegetables, bizarre log cabins, products that don't exist. AI-generated images are creating new forms of clickbait and causing some users to doubt what's real.
title: AI-generated spam is starting to fill social media. Here's why

description: Federal regulators say all airline passengers must be able to evacuate a plane within 90 seconds. The FAA reauthorization bill would require the agency to reconsider its testing standards.
title: FAA bill would force the agency to craft 'real world' rules for airplane evacuations

description: When Thorsten Siess was in graduate school, he came up with the idea for a heart device that's now been used in hundreds of thousands of patients around the world.
title: He invented a successful medical device as a student. Here's his advice for new grads

description: A rescue operation was ongoing Tuesday, and it was unclear how many people may still be trapped from the collapse during heavy rain and thunderstorms.
title: Billboard collapses onto people in Mumbai, killing at least 14

description: The detonation marked a major step in freeing the Dali, which has been stuck among the wreckage since it crashed into one of the bridge's support columns shortly after leaving Baltimore on March 26.
title: Collapsed Baltimore bridge span comes down with a boom

description: The Carol Shields Prize for Fiction is a relatively new literary award given to women and nonbinary authors. This year's winner is V.V. Ganeshananthan for her book Brotherless Night.
title: 'Brotherless Night,' an ambitious novel about Sri Lankan civil war, wins $150K prize
